 Syntax:  .sthink <user> <mess>

Results:  Allows you to express thoughts visibly to a specific person
          privately. <user> is the person you are thinking to.

Example:  Typing  .sthink necros hmm, this cygnus is cool
          will show --> <your name> thinks . o O ( hmm, this cygnus is cool )
          to necros.

See also: think
